 * Hardware Cursor for Trident utilizing XAA Cursor code.
 * Written by Alan Hourihane <alanh@@fairlite.demon.co.uk>
 * Modified for Chips and Technologies by David Bateman <dbateman@@eng.uts.edu.au>
